thread.title: Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text:
Popular styles and sizes had some stock shortages, and I noticed they don't carry more recent styles of some brands. However, if they have the shoes you want then just go ahead and grab them!
The prices are really good and the shipping is unbelievable. I ordered 2 pairs of shoes on Friday and they arrived at my door in Sydney, Australia at lunchtime on Monday! That is quicker than most local couriers can manage...
